==Finnish==
alkoholismi
===Noun===
#[[alkoholiriippuvuus]]

===Usage notes===
While the term is eligible for both [[addiction]] and [[poisoning]] by alcohol, it is mostly used about the addiction. The acute alcohol poisoning is called ''alkoholimyrkytys''.
